727357f-a.title: Queens: Maspeth Avenue - 56th Street
727357f-a.text:
Maspeth Ave., north side, on the line of about 56th Street,
about two hundred feet north ofEnspeth Ave., showing the burial
plot of the Furman family containing thirteen head and thirteen
foot stones.
September 1929.
Views 1 and 2.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
